      <title>美联储米兰：采用稳定币可能会给利率带来下行压力</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/feds-miran-stablecoin-adoption-could-put-downward-pressure-interest-rates-2025-11-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事斯蒂芬·米兰周五表示，如果稳定币最终得到广泛采用，这可能意味着央行需要将短期利率保持在低于正常水平的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/feds-miran-stablecoin-adoption-could-put-downward-pressure-interest-rates-2025-11-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Nov 2025 20:00:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
