      <title>泛欧交易所降低购买雅典交易所的接受门槛</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/euronext-lowers-acceptance-threshold-buying-athens-bourse-2025-11-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泛欧交易所运营商泛欧交易所周五表示，为了控制雅典证券交易所，它将把接受门槛从 67% 降低到 50%，再加上一股投票权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/euronext-lowers-acceptance-threshold-buying-athens-bourse-2025-11-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Nov 2025 19:16:02 GMT</pubDate>
