      <title>瑞银将清算受第一品牌破产影响的奥康纳资金</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-liquidate-oconnor-funds-hit-by-first-brands-bankruptcy-2025-11-07/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团周五表示，由于对破产的美国汽车零部件供应商第一品牌集团(First Brands Group)的投资蒙受损失，该集团正在逐步缩减其对冲基金部门奥康纳(O&#39;Connor)运营的投资基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-liquidate-oconnor-funds-hit-by-first-brands-bankruptcy-2025-11-07/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Nov 2025 14:55:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
